Industrial Equity ( Pacific ) Ltd , Hong Kong investment firm , said raised stake Calmat Co 1,480,830 share , 9.8 pct total outstanding common stock , 1,217,230 share , 8.0 pct .
In filing Securities Exchange Commission , Industrial Equity , principally owned Brierley Investments Ltd , publicly held New Zealand firm , said bought 263,600 Calmat common share Feb 17 March 9 13.1 mln dlrs .
It said bought stock investment purpose , may raise stake 15 pct .
